plan to prioritise diversity in sound as well as a steadfast dedication to highlighting fresh acts (like on its BMI stage, where up-and-coming acts like Annie DiRusso and Beauty School Dropout are met with fans who sing along to every single word) the festival proves its dedication to just putting the music first, and the fans Lollapalooza draws in反映这项努力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-olivia-rodrigo-korn-and-more-lead-lollapalooza-2025-line-up-3847245">萨布丽娜木匠，奥利维亚·罗德里戈（Olivia Rodrigo），科恩（Korn）和更多铅Lollapalooza 2025阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
